  "text": "Theorem 2 (Asymptotic stability for 1D cubic NLS, [CITATION_1] ). Let s > 1. There exists \u03b4 > 0 such that for any u 0 \u2208 L 2 with x s u 0 \u2208 L 2 and x s (u 0 \u2212 Q) L 2 \u2264 \u03b4, the solution u of (2) with initial data u 0 satisfies, for t 1,",
